{"tid":2489550,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 花椒麻辣豬頸肉炒意粉 脆脆古古力泡芙","createTime":"2021-04-15T04:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T05:22:01.000Z","uid":33359,"like":12,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"78321d7f8197d952b11c72a5e8e3af79b676e8af","tid":2489550,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u0kQB1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu0kQB1c.jpg&h=219aea69&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n8Xb5Uz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn8Xb5Uz.jpg&h=f6c29325&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UAoVN7W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUAoVN7W.jpg&h=c900ddcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個意粉一食係鹽西味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後先慢慢有花椒味滲出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n意粉個油份岩岩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔會太乾太濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n豬頸肉很香有咬口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外仲加咗泡芙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n泡芙外層好脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲係岩岩係雪櫃拎出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入面個filling好似雪糕咁既口感好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落個腎臟好c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"875c34907871e996f9f78dfc0bb80b1b76398d33","tid":2489550,"uid":59703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:18:24.000Z","msg":"早食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1583147d6b76e6819441c7c82b4b033b4378d1","tid":2489550,"uid":304460,"like":0